udas Priest)</a>在蒙特利尔开始了他们最新的北美巡演。请参阅下面晚上的录像。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/judas-priest-rob-halford-heavy-metal-3594311">犹大牧师传奇人物罗布·哈尔福德：“出柜是以正确的方式发生的 - 这不是有预谋的”</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨天（9 月 13 日），这支重金属乐队在贝尔中心继续支持 2024 年专辑《Invincible Shield》，两个月后，他们的欧洲之旅于 7 月在土耳其伊斯坦布尔结束。</p><p>当晚的歌单混合了《无敌之盾》和九张经典专辑中深受粉丝喜爱的歌曲。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Judas Priest - You’ve Got Another Thing Coming（加拿大蒙特利尔 QC 现场直播；2024 年 9 月 13 日）4K" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CsuKNGr4ooI?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Judas Priest - Turbo Lover - 蒙特利尔 2024 年 9 月 13 日" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/M7Ha6rsARLU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Judas Priest - 止痛药 @ Centre Bell (蒙特利尔 2024-09-13)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/IHJOKmQvCm0?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="犹大牧师 - 地狱中的圣徒（加拿大蒙特利尔 13/9/2024）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Z-lXIUCjgWY?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h3> Judas Priest 在蒙特利尔举行的“Invincible Shield”巡演日期的曲目列表是（来自<a href="https://www.setlist.fm/setlist/judas-priest/2024/centre-bell-montreal-qc-canada-35645e3.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Setlist.fm</a> ）：</h3><p> <strong>&#39;惊恐发作&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“你还有另一件事要发生”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;速射&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“触犯法律”</strong><br /> <strong>《乘风破浪》</strong><br /> <strong>《爱咬一口》</strong><br /> <strong>《恶魔之子》</strong><br /> <strong>《地狱里的圣人》</strong><br /> <strong>《角之王冠》</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;罪人&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>《涡轮爱好者》</strong><br /> <strong>《无敌之盾》</strong><br /> <strong>“变革的受害者”</strong><br /> <strong>“The Green Manalishi（带有两爪皇冠）”（弗利特伍德麦克封面）</strong><br /> <strong>“止痛药”</strong></p><p><strong>安可：</strong><br /> <strong>《恶人》/《电眼》</strong><br /> <strong>“皮革的地狱”</strong><br /> <strong>《午夜后的生活》</strong></p><p>同一天，乐队发行了 50 周年纪念版《Rocka Rolla》，其中包含由长期合作者兼制作人 Tom Allom 创作的全新混音。</p><p>这项努力源于乐队在 2022 年得知唱片公司 Gull Records 的所有者（该公司发行了乐队的前两张专辑“Rocka Rolla”和“Sad Wings of Destiny”）热衷于向他们出售这些专辑的母带和出版权。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_27Td4vPnO/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; he